• Designed and implemented a Verilog-based ATM finite state machine supporting authentication, withdrawals, lockout protection, and balance enquiry.

• Built a Python verification framework that automatically generates testbenches, executes RTL simulations using Icarus Verilog, and parses simulation outputs.

• Developed randomized and edge-case test suites with state and transition coverage reporting, achieving high verification coverage across ATM workflows.

• Created an HTML dashboard for simulation reports, coverage metrics, and waveform inspection.
